github_body:
General changes:
* #424 Reworked the front page to make it more clear that MDT import is a feature. Also updated some information and added a dungeon selector so you can more easily jump to a demo route.

Mapping changes:
* #252 Operation: Mechagon Workshop: added missing enemies. Also fixed various issues in the admin section.
